author: Nick Roush
title: Nobody in the world is having more fun than THIS GUY
text:
Posted in Football , Main | 1 Response 
College Gameday is at Clemson today, where Hurricane Joaquin has turned the place into a party. Thousands have showed up, even though the game doesn’t kickoff till 8:00, and I don’t know if there’s a place I’d rather be, or a person I’d rather party with than this guy. 
— Busted Coverage (@bustedcoverage) October 3, 2015 
I don’t know what it is, but I could watch this all day. Article written by Nick Roush "Look upon the doughnut, and not upon the hole." @RoushKSR One response to “Nobody in the world is having more fun than THIS GUY” Vettemandoo October 3, 2015 at 11:25 am | Permalink | Reply 
Can’t you see the family resemblance… it’s Booby Petrino’s younger bro. Post Comment - New and Improved (not really, it just works now)
